import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import Section from './Section'


function Home() {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Section
          title="Model S"
          description= "Order Online for Touchless Delivery"
          backgroundImd="model-s.jpg"
        />
      <Section />
      <Section />
      <Section />
    </Container>
    
  )
}

export default Home

const Container = styled.div`
      height: 100vh;
`
